# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# HostMasters — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and fill in values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Core ──────────────────────────────────────────
NEXTAUTH_URL="https://hostmasters.es"
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=""                    # openssl rand -base64 32
DATABASE_URL=""                       # postgresql://...@neon.tech/...

# ── Stripe (Payments + Connect) ──────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=""                  # sk_live_...
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=""            # pk_live_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=""             # whsec_...
STRIPE_BASIC_PRICE_ID=""             # price_... (€89/mo)
STRIPE_MID_PRICE_ID=""               # price_... (€159/mo)
STRIPE_PREMIUM_PRICE_ID=""          # price_... (€269/mo)

# ── Resend (Email) ────────────────────────────────
RESEND_API_KEY=""                     # re_...
EMAIL_FROM="HostMasters <noreply@hostmasters.es>"

# ── Anthropic (AI) ────────────────────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""                  # sk-ant-...

# ── Twilio (SMS) ──────────────────────────────────
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=""
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=""
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=""               # +34...

# ── Sentry (Error Tracking) ──────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=""            # https://...@sentry.io/...
SENTRY_DSN=""                        # same as above (server-side)
SENTRY_ORG="hostmasters"
SENTRY_PROJECT="hostmasters-web"

# ── Cron Protection ──────────────────────────────
CRON_SECRET=""                        # openssl rand -hex 32

# ── Notifications ─────────────────────────────────
ADMIN_EMAIL="admin@hostmasters.es"
MONITOR_WEBHOOK_URL=""               # Slack/Discord webhook for AI Monitor alerts

# ── Analytics ─────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=""                  # GA4 measurement ID
NEXT_PUBLIC_META_PIXEL_ID=""

# ── Future Integrations ──────────────────────────
# PRICELABS_API_KEY=""               # Dynamic pricing
# NUKI_API_TOKEN=""                  # Smart Lock
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=""              # Voice AI (VAGF calls)
# ELEVENLABS_WEBHOOK_SECRET=""       # ElevenLabs webhook validation
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_EN=""             # Agent IDs per language
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_PT=""
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_ES=""
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_DE=""
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_FR=""
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_NL=""
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_DA=""
# ELEVENLABS_AGENT_NO=""
# REVOLUT_API_KEY=""                 # One-time service payments
# WHATSAPP_BUSINESS_TOKEN=""         # WhatsApp Business API

# ── CRM Integration ──────────────────────────────
# INTEGRATION_SECRET=""              # CRM lead form endpoint token
# NEXT_PUBLIC_INTEGRATION_SECRET=""  # Public variant for embeds

# ── Optional Overrides ───────────────────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=""             # Public URL (defaults to NEXTAUTH_URL)
# VAGF_ANALYSIS_MODEL=""            # Override AI model for VAGF (default: claude-haiku-4-5-20251001)
# STAY_CHAT_MODEL=""                # Override AI model for Guest Stay Chat
